(blast-zone 100 100 30)" :explanation "Build the circle record from the impact point and blast radius. The record can be handed to other geom predicates." :meta "geom/circle is the correct verb because it packages center and radius into an identity-preserving value. Passing three raw numbers around is possible but loses the structural fact that they are a circle.")
