(< (abs (- total pieces)) 1e-9)" :invariant "∀ r > 0, l ≥ r. cone-surface(r, l) = π·r² + π·r·l" :meta "Decomposable sum: the surface splits cleanly into base and side. If broken, a term is missing or its coefficient is wrong. See book-of-math ch 4 (surface area of a cone).")
